Distribution.
Known from a total of eight islands in the Mercury Group (Middle, Green and Korapuki Is.), Alderman Group (Half, Hongiora, Ruamahuanui and Ruamahuati Is.) and the Ohinau Group (Old Man Rock), all off the east coast of the Coromandel Peninsula (
